title: Why Did the Chicken Waddle Off Set?
itunes:title: Why Did the Chicken Waddle Off Set?
description:
Why Did the Chicken Waddle Off Set? 


PANTS with Kate Moennig and Leisha Hailey

Produced by Melisa D. Monts and Diamond MPrint Productions

Edited by Diane Kang 

 

Leisha compares her presence on set to a chicken wandering in and out. Kate gets harassed by summer mosquitos. Leisha then helps Kate articulate her distaste for “shoegazing” music and the use of the word “vibes”. It’s a real vibe, man.
